USC - DTI ROI Summary Measures v1

Source: R/data.R
DTIROI_V1.Rd

USC - DTI ROI Summary Measures v1 data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(DTIROI_V1)

Format

A data frame with 976 observations and 243 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 123, ..., 5295

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • EXAMDATE Examination Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • VERSION numeric Version Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • VISNAME character

  • VISITNO numeric Visit Range value: 3, ..., 50

  • LONIUID_1 numeric LONI Image ID for FA Range value: 299595, ..., 848440

  • LONIUID_2 numeric LONI Image ID for MD Range value: 299814, ..., 848443

  • LONIUID_3 numeric LONI Image ID for RD Range value: 359669, ..., 848449

  • LONIUID_4 numeric LONI Image ID for AD Range value: 297755, ..., 848446

  • RUNDATE Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • STATUS character Status , with options: Complete
